In preferences for SSL set RSA Keylist to:
  UNIX/Linux: 127.0.0.1,443,http,/path/to/snakeoil2.key
  Windows:    127.0.0.1,443,http,c:\path\to\snakeoil2.key
  
To get to preferences do the following:
- right click an SSL request
- select "Protocol Preferences"
- select "Transport Layer Security"
- select "RSA Keys List"
- Enter the information above
